{"tid":1261153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【情報】小AI:勇士隊醫告訴KD只是小腿拉傷 就算上場，最多傷勢加重","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T08:24:43.000Z","uid":235537,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65646231fef566de86659a624013504974b53a8f","tid":1261153,"uid":235537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"近期，勇士球員Iguodala做客節目時候曝出猛料。Iguodala表示勇士高管一直都有向球員隱瞞傷情的惡習。Iguodala談到了去年西決自己的情況，當時的Iguodala遭遇了腿骨折，而勇士並沒有對外透露實情，反而說只是骨頭挫傷而已，這讓當時的Iguodala受到了很多的壓力。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7uWdzg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7uWdzg.png&h=32859e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在談到Kevin Durant的時候，Iguodala表示勇士的隊醫一直告訴Kevin Durant他只是小腿拉傷，和跟腱沒有半毛錢關係，甚至隊醫還告訴Kevin Durant就算帶傷上場，最多也就是小腿拉傷的傷勢加重，Kevin Durant的跟腱會安然無恙的。結果呢？Kevin Durant打了一節的時間，跟腱斷了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nba.nbcsports.com/2019/06/25/andre-iguodala-i-broke-my-leg-last-year-but-warriors-called-it-just-a-bruise/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnba.nbcsports.com%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fandre-iguodala-i-broke-my-leg-last-year-but-warriors-called-it-just-a-bruise%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=292b7d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nba.nbcsports.com/2019/06/25/andre-iguodala-i-broke-my-leg-last-year-but-warriors-called-it-just-a-bruise/</a><br />\n<br />\n這樣的球團手段真是好離譜,毀左一個超巨KD的未來發展同對歷史地位的成就追逐,希望以後不要再發生這種悲劇了,球員得好好保護自己啊,不論哪隊都一樣"},{"pid":"f5ee5069c880aaabb3612a009e1d4f95c0673c3b","tid":1261153,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65646231fef566de86659a624013504974b53a8f","tid":1261153,"uid":235537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"近期，勇士球員Iguodala做客節目時候曝出猛料。Iguodala表示勇士高管一直都有向球員隱瞞傷情的惡習。Iguodala談到了去年西決自己的情況，當時的Iguodala遭遇了腿骨折，而勇士並沒有對外透露實情，反而說只是骨頭挫傷而已，這讓當時的Iguodala受到了很多的壓力。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7uWdzg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum